{"tid":1503983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"集中討論發夢步兵戰陣","createTime":"2019-08-25T06:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T11:23:40.000Z","uid":121146,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1d24714af1076a714b4c4db95d671c98382d89d1","tid":1503983,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:57:06.000Z","msg":"速狗突然單兵衝入  每次都拉到為數不少既義士<br />\n為預防日後一衝即散  義士被拉入集中型<br />\n我地必須要傾好陣式去應對<br />\n<br />\n狗有受訓、有耳機  動作連成一體  <br />\n義士們  每個人都只係個體  <br />\n我地冇大台  通訊做唔到即時通話  <br />\n亦無可能一夫當關<br />\n但同時  都有應對方法<br />\n<br />\n電影  孤軍雄心  正正就話比我地知  點以雜牌兵  打嬴正規軍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u1vWK2yf9Y0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Du1vWK2yf9Y0&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=4007b5ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u1vWK2yf9Y0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RL8gGnK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRL8gGnK.png&h=3e8bc0b3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黃軍必須分開兩個列陣<br />\n前線要有心理準備抵受催淚彈攻擊<br />\n不衝  不前進  不散  不退  用雨傘抗住<br />\n同時保持後方與狗距離   令催淚彈射唔到後面<br />\n<br />\n速狗衝埋黎  有兩個結果<br />\n1．速狗單兵諗住打無雙  前線擋得住  <br />\n黃軍後方要立即衝前  以人海壓制<br />\n<br />\n2．速狗衝前  長盾狗貼近  <br />\n前線等速狗走近時  立即跑向後方陣營  <br />\n後排與前線接應後  待速狗接近時  一齊衝上去<br />\n<br />\n注意：<br />\n作為一個見義勇為既香港人  要捉冒警狗<br />\n如無法出示委任證<br />\n女士冒警狗可經由女士們搜身  <br />\n男士冒警狗可脫衣檢查<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如發現有委任證在衣物內  請禮貌放人</span><br />\n冇編號、冇委任證既狗  全部扎起<br />\n有義士被捉  大家即時商議點救<br />\n不圍  不單兵掉石仔  <br />\n唔好個個走哂前面  一放催淚彈就鳥獸散<br />\n前線擋  後援休息、支援  齊上齊落  <br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93237bea11213f69b474e558718ad83dbf36d3bf","tid":1503983,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:00:56.000Z","msg":"仲有  我地唔係打狗  係捉狗 <br />\n佢衝上黎打你  你唔係拎雨傘打返佢<br />\n而係捉住佢隻手  拉佢入黎  <br />\n切忌單兵衝前  做咩都要跟大隊"},{"pid":"98f4e03d7f4c80fb9ac95d5a6b9b2b13df32bcc6","tid":1503983,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:02:24.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7995e286f87fae98ca50e261e8f806d31f77c30","tid":1503983,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:02:55.000Z","msg":"例個係火槍戰術，最好參考翻冷兵器戰術"},{"pid":"cb630042de15a9a3c236c249c032395ee6190a4f","tid":1503983,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7995e286f87fae98ca50e261e8f806d31f77c30","tid":1503983,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:02:55.000Z","msg":"例個係火槍戰術，最好參考翻冷兵器戰術"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:03:32.000Z","msg":"討論討論  大家一齊諗  然後人人跟住做  一個都唔可以再比狗拉"},{"pid":"16ad5e5860fae2a49b26e1afeeba1c8e9c97a911","tid":1503983,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:04:58.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15eae162a9b5e5ce699d2a3ff75e0551a1d68698","tid":1503983,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:05:34.000Z","msg":"如果先布袋彈再衝？"},{"pid":"482f37896a850c2145a1b63e5416a8eb4af465ec","tid":1503983,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:07:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oxNtm9AbaFs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoxNtm9AbaFs&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=abe71fe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oxNtm9AbaFs</a>"},{"pid":"a1e643f30da4e03c0c63ee62adb5c51a047f13ef","tid":1503983,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:11:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/k9QbVVAT5hc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fk9QbVVAT5hc&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=bbb4b795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/k9QbVVAT5hc</a>"},{"pid":"a17e58c5461c65ca9ee316d377f7c9e96a5f04e6","tid":1503983,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:18:49.000Z","msg":"但我地對手係羅馬陣法"},{"pid":"2d2d4be3b97110de7bf7e15f99d4b039a263afa6","tid":1503983,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:19:13.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0mmSi0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0mmSi0.jpg&h=e2509c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 官逼民反，民不得不反<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dJNfyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dJNfyS</a>"},{"pid":"8a5604cd354514661460fbb05d0c3ecaaef28eac","tid":1503983,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:20:26.000Z","msg":"等速狗衝到半路  前線全體回防後方<br />\n後方與前線接合後  等速狗一到  就衝<br />\n目的： <br />\n1．拖長速狗跑步時間<br />\n2．拉長速狗同長盾狗距離"},{"pid":"5e323037b952582e6a13e1d7b7ac41032d832f76","tid":1503983,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15eae162a9b5e5ce699d2a3ff75e0551a1d68698","tid":1503983,"uid":43081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:05:34.000Z","msg":"如果先布袋彈再衝？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:20:59.000Z","msg":"等速狗衝到半路 前線全體回防後方<br />\n後方與前線接合後 等速狗一到 就衝<br />\n目的： <br />\n1．拖長速狗跑步時間<br />\n2．拉長速狗同長盾狗距離"},{"pid":"be3f901bd7f9eded5386e35913e559437e912c29","tid":1503983,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"482f37896a850c2145a1b63e5416a8eb4af465ec","tid":1503983,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:07:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oxNtm9AbaFs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoxNtm9AbaFs&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=abe71fe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oxNtm9AbaFs</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:21:10.000Z","msg":"但我地對手係羅馬陣法"},{"pid":"4efa3d5b1f6e0044f27550e93f703344a08b4565","tid":1503983,"uid":45519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:22:26.000Z","msg":"雜牌軍最重要係士氣同有少少指揮，有時多幾個人一齊嗌衝然後上前，成個陣勢就會唔同咗。"},{"pid":"47155710fe0dd18f4d45861c49691457f9afb667","tid":1503983,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4efa3d5b1f6e0044f27550e93f703344a08b4565","tid":1503983,"uid":45519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:22:26.000Z","msg":"雜牌軍最重要係士氣同有少少指揮，有時多幾個人一齊嗌衝然後上前，成個陣勢就會唔同咗。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"係  所以我地既陣法一定要單一<br />\n我提出既陣型只有一個<br />\n進可攻  退可守  <br />\n總之前線擋唔住  就回防<br />\n前線擋得住  後面就上前進攻<br />\n捉到狗  就扎起放係前線、後援中間  <br />\n咁班狗就唔會再敢鳩放"},{"pid":"71600ef3731fbd7520c1d8f3f5ef74c3421005c1","tid":1503983,"uid":251556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:28:03.000Z","msg":"最主要係要有指揮 無人統一指令 一盤散沙點樣衝"},{"pid":"9bb2d4d309b0652d2a93b0bb548237f0538311a6","tid":1503983,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:32:01.000Z","msg":"所以指令唔可以太複雜<br />\n應該咁講  後援直頭係唔需要指令<br />\n只要前線仲擋緊  就衝上去<br />\n只要前線退  就接人再衝<br />\n所以前線一定要傾好邊個做決定退  <br />\n一聲退  全部向後跑 <br />\n冇其他指示要做  咁簡單應該唔難？"},{"pid":"109a24eeedc7ddf20fa392185793f5c82e6fed65","tid":1503983,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:32:11.000Z","msg":"所以指令唔可以太複雜<br />\n應該咁講 後援直頭係唔需要指令<br />\n只要前線仲擋緊 就衝上去<br />\n只要前線退 就接人再衝<br />\n所以前線一定要傾好邊個做決定退 <br />\n一聲退 全部向後跑 <br />\n冇其他指示要做 咁簡單應該唔難？"},{"pid":"cf3773c2ced1c30df84e321699836d2e7bcb6188","tid":1503983,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47155710fe0dd18f4d45861c49691457f9afb667","tid":1503983,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4efa3d5b1f6e0044f27